GetLatestTinderbox
==================

get-latest-tinderbox is a python script that fetches urls and related
information from Mozilla's FTP builds:

http://stage.mozilla.org/pub/mozilla.org/firefox/tinderbox-builds/

Alternately, a URL may be specified.
